content.value: Made from 100% recycled fleece, this Full Zip Sweater Fleece is the perfect companion to chiller days. Soft and warm, the low-bulk is perfect as a jacket in the city, or layer under a shell for added warmth. Fair Trade Certified with a flattering silhouette and anti-pilling, anti-abrasion composition.
Material: 100% Recycled Polyester fleece (made from recycled water bottles)
Anti Pilling, anti abrasion sweater fleece fabric
Thermal insulation fleece interior, double brushed for ultimate softness
Secure chest pocket (fits iPhone XS)
Microfleece lined inner collar for soft comfort and warmth

Made with Recycled Polyester - Recycled polyester dramatically lowers its environmental impact by diverting used plastic from landfills and oceans, while consuming much less energy than virgin materials
Bluesign & Oeko-Tex certified
Model is 6'0 wearing a size Medium
Machine wash cold, inside out with like colors.  Do not use fabric softener.  Only non-chlorine bleach when needed. Tumble dry low, do not iron, do not dry clean.
